10:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Prezi AI is best suited for speakers, educators, creative presenters, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Visme, meanwhile, shines for marketers, educators, business professionals, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2009, Prezi AI describes itself as \"Dynamic presentation platform with AI-enhanced zooming and non-linear storytelling.\" Visme, established in 2013, positions itself as \"Design platform for creating presentations, infographics, and visual content.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
11:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Visme** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (7.0 vs 6.0), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Prezi AI is a poor choice — far from it. Prezi AI excels in its own right, particularly for speakers and educators.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value excellent for data visualization, go with Visme. If unique zooming presentation style matters more to you, Prezi AI is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
